jobcoach.projectDescription: Mobile application to help active job seekers find relevant opportunities through an assistant.

details.projectInfo: JobCoach's focus is to help active job seekers to find relevant opportunities (jobs & companies), and assist them to be more effective in the process. The mobile application should be based on what Viadeo already have + some extra features that will make the difference

SpotAngels.projectDescription: Mapping startup enabling cars to understand cities infrastructure.

details.projectInfo: SpotAngels is a mapping startup enabling cars to understand cities infrastructure. We start with parking. We build real time parking maps with a spot by spot granularity. We license our data to the automotive industry to help drivers find parking and avoid tickets. We developed a consumer app that saves drivers from parking tickets. Through the app, our community helps us keep the data updated.
